qDef.qDef:
//=([Shelf Price]-[Promo Price])/[Shelf Price]


Pick
(
	$(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD)
       
    
        //CM
        
        ,
        (ONLY ({$< [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, $(v_Switch_Option_Measure_Group) >}[Shelf Price] )
        -
        ONLY ({$< [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, $(v_Switch_Option_Measure_Group) >}[Promo Price] ))
        /
        ONLY ({$< [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, $(v_Switch_Option_Measure_Group) >}[Shelf Price] )
    
      
      //YTD
             
        ,(ONLY ({$<  [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, $(v_Switch_Option_Measure_Group) , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}  >}[Shelf Price] )
        -
        ONLY ({$< [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, $(v_Switch_Option_Measure_Group) , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}  >}[Promo Price] ))
        /
        ONLY ({$< [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, $(v_Switch_Option_Measure_Group) , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)}  >}[Shelf Price] )
     
        
)

byMeasureDef.label: Promo
